                    <h1>Careers</h1>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Polaris Automation is currently looking to add to our team of engineers.  If you are looking for a career in a challenging environment where your achievements are recognized then Polaris Automation has what you are looking for.  We believe that our most important asset is our staff.  Polaris Automation focuses much attention on ensuring that we create careers not jobs.  It is our hope that Polaris Automation is the last career selection that you will ever make.</span></p>
<p>We are currently looking for:</p>
<p>Electrical/Controls Engineers<br />
IT Engineers<br />
Electrical Designers<br />
Project Managers<br />
Mechanical Engineers</p>
<p>Please submit your resume to <a href="mailto:careers@polarisautomation.com">careers@polarisautomation.com</a></p>

